data.description: GORGEOUS UPDATED SMART HOME! BRAND NEW IMPACT WINDOWS JUST INSTALLED!  Pride in ownership shows on this bright beautiful home in the upscale neighborhood of Savannah's Golf Community.  Home has amazing water views all living spaces with water on 2 sides w/golf course views of 10th green. Cambria quartz countertops in the chief kitchen, high end gas appliances, confection oven, built-in microwave.  Voice remote activated lights, blinds, music, LED pool lighting & more! Large master bedroom, large shower, double vanities & sitting area. Outdoor shower w/ summer kitchen with large enclosed lanai for entertaining. Hot tub heated with propane, tropical salt system pool.  House generator, separate electric box, BRAND new HVAC only 4 months old. Nothing more to say except come see before its GONE! Check out the upgrades flyer attached showing all the amazing features of this beautiful home.
